text: Nancy Olson (born April 14, 1928) is an American actress. She was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Supporting Actress in Sunset Boulevard (1950). Other movies including The Absent-Minded Professor and Airport 1975 (1974). She has mostly retired from acting. Olson was born in Milwaukee, Wisconsin. == References == Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:1928 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Milwaukee
